---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@2.5.1/dist/flowbite.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<MainLayout 
  title="Integration Solutions Agency & Digital Asset Management in the Cloud" 
  description="Partner with our expert Laravel development agency for integration solutions and cloud-based digital asset management. Build scalable, cost-effective platforms with full ownership, surpassing Shopify, Magento, and PrestaShop."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 text-white">
    <div class="py-16 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none">Integration Solutions Agency for Laravel Development</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-xl font-normal">Our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> specializes in <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong>, delivering custom Laravel platforms with seamless API integrations, full ownership, and scalability. Outperform Shopify, Magento, and PrestaShop with lower costs and unmatched flexibility.</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
        <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-indigo-700 bg-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300">Get Your Free Store Setup <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a>
        <a href="#features" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white border border-white rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-indigo-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-100">Explore Integration Solutions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 py-12">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Why Choose Our Integration Solutions Agency?</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-12">
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cloud-Based Digital Asset Management</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Our <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> solutions ensure secure, scalable storage and seamless access to your assets, integrated via Laravel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Seamless API Integrations</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">As a leading <strong>integration solutions agency</strong>, we connect your platform with Instagram, payment gateways, and more using Laravel’s robust APIs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Own Your Platform</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Avoid Shopify’s fees with our Laravel solutions, offering full ownership and control over your data and platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Scalable Cloud Solutions</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Our <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> scales effortlessly, handling millions of SKUs with Elasticsearch and APIs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cost-Effective Setup</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Start with a free store setup from our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong>, avoiding subscription costs of Shopify or Magento.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 mb-4 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16zm0 14a6 6 0 110-12 6 6 0 010 12z"/></svg>
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Social Media Integration</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Seamlessly connect your store to Instagram and other platforms with our Laravel-based integration solutions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Shopify Alternatives Section -->
      <div class="py-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Shopify Alternatives with Our Integration Solutions</h2>
        <p class="text-center mb-12 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Looking for a better eCommerce solution? Our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> leverages Laravel and <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> to deliver flexible, cost-effective platforms that surpass Shopify, BigCommerce, and WooCommerce.</p>
        <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
          <!-- BigCommerce -->
          <h3 id="accordion-1">
            <button type="button" class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium text-left text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 rounded-t-lg dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-800" data-accordion-target="#accordion-1-body" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="accordion-1-body">
              <span>BigCommerce</span>
              <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            </button>
          </h3>
          <div id="accordion-1-body" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-1">
            <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <p class="mb-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">BigCommerce offers scalability but lacks the customization of our Laravel-based <strong>integration solutions agency</strong>. Our cloud solutions provide full control and no subscription fees.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Choose our <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> at <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-600 underline dark:text-blue-400">Laravel Company</a> for tailored platforms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Additional platforms (WooCommerce, Wix, etc.) follow similar structure with keyword integration -->
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 dark:focus:ring-blue-900">Discover Our Integration Solutions <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Laravel Development Services -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-12">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Our Integration Solutions & Cloud DAM Services</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">As a premier <strong>integration solutions agency</strong>, we offer <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> and custom Laravel solutions for scalable, secure eCommerce platforms.</p>
      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Custom Integration Solutions</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> builds tailored platforms with seamless third-party integrations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cloud-Based DAM</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Leverage <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> for secure, scalable asset storage and retrieval.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Platform Migration</h5>
          <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400">Migrate from Shopify or Magento to our Laravel solutions with expert support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300">Contact Our Integration Agency</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">How Our Integration Solutions Work</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-0 md:flex md:justify-between">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Choose Your Plan</h4>
          <p>Collaborate with our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> to select a free or premium plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Integrate Assets</h4>
          <p>Utilize <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> to upload and manage products via APIs or CSV.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-blue-600 text-xl font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Launch Your Platform</h4>
          <p>Go live with a fully integrated, cloud-based Laravel platform tailored by our agency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-12">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">What Clients Say About Our Integration Solutions</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <figure class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
          <blockquote>
            <p class="text-2xl italic font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">“This <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> reduced our costs by 80% with cloud-based DAM and Laravel.”</p>
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center mt-6 space-x-3">
            <img class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full" src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/michael-gough.png" alt="Sarah L., Founder of ModaCo, praising integration solutions">
            <div class="flex items-center divide-x-2 divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700">
              <cite class="pr-3 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sarah L.</cite>
              <cite class="pl-3 text-sm font-light text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Founder, ModaCo</cite>
            </div>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <!-- Additional testimonials with similar keyword integration -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
        <h2 id="faq1">
          <button class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium text-left text-gray-500 border border-gray-200 rounded-t-lg" data-accordion-target="#faq1-body">Is your integration solutions agency cheaper than Shopify?</button>
        </h2>
        <div id="faq1-body" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="faq1">
          <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200">Yes, our <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> offers free setup and no monthly fees, unlike Shopify.</div>
        </div>
        <h2 id="faq2">
          <button class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium text-left text-gray-500 border border-gray-200" data-accordion-target="#faq2-body">How does digital asset management in the cloud work?</button>
        </h2>
        <div id="faq2-body" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="faq2">
          <div class="p-5 border border-b-0 border-gray-200">Our <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> provides secure storage, easy access, and seamless integration with your Laravel platform.</div>
        </div>
        <!-- Additional FAQs with keyword integration -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section id="get-started" class="py-16 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-center">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Transform with Our Integration Solutions Agency?</h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-xl">Leverage <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong> and custom Laravel platforms to surpass Shopify, Magento, and PrestaShop.</p>
      <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-white text-indigo-700 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg">Start Your Free Store Today</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-8">
    <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center">
      <p class="mb-4">© 2025 <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="underline">Laravel Company</a> - Premier <strong>integration solutions agency</strong> for <strong>digital asset management in the cloud</strong>.</p>
      <a href="https://laravelcompany.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Contact Our Integration Experts</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</MainLayout>
